OL,3,C'It's because we care': Families
OL,4,Cfighting for justice after maternity
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FITV News Central correspondent
OL,8,FCharlotte Cross met two families
OL,9,Fcampaigning for change after maternity
OL,10,Ffailings
OL,12,FFamilies fighting for change after
OL,13,Ftheir babies died due to have revealed
OL,14,Fwhy they continue to campaign through
OL,15,Ftheir grief.
OL,17,FRhiannon and Richard Davies' daughter
OL,18,FKate died shortly after being born at
OL,19,Fthe Shrewsbury & Telford NHS Trust in
OL,20,F2009.
