OL,3,C'It's because we care': Families
OL,4,Cfighting for justice after maternity
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,F"Seeing the same patterns of failings
OL,8,Fover and over again, causing the same
OL,9,Fdevastating outcomes.
OL,11,F"There was no appetite to put the
OL,12,Fpicture together, to create change, to
OL,13,Flearn, to prevent avoidable harm. If
OL,14,Fanything, it was very much the
OL,15,Fopposite - to cover up, lie, remove
OL,16,Fnotes, you know, play it down."
OL,18,FThese allegations of a 'culture of
OL,19,Fcover-up' have now been supported by
OL,20,Fthe Parliamentary and Health Service
OL,21,FOmbudsman.
