OL,3,C'It's because we care': Families
OL,4,Cfighting for justice after maternity
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FRebecca Hilsenrath, the Chief
OL,8,FExecutive of the Ombudsman, says it is
OL,9,Fleading to avoidable deaths - and
OL,10,Fkeeping the truth from grieving
OL,11,Ffamilies.JShe said: "Over the past
OL,12,Ffour years, we've received about 700
OL,13,Fcomplaints about maternity.
OL,15,F"Instead of there being an open
OL,16,Fculture of proper investigation and
OL,17,Frecognition, there's often been a
OL,18,Ffailure to investigate and a failure
OL,19,Fto properly recognise and apologise to
OL,20,Fthe families."
