OL,3,C'It's because we care': Families
OL,4,Cfighting for justice after maternity
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FLast week, the outgoing Chief
OL,8,FExecutive, Rob Behrens CBE, spoke to
OL,9,FGood Morning Britain about what he
OL,10,Fcalled a "damaging", "cover-up
OL,11,Fculture" in hospitals.
OL,13,FHe said this leads to hospitals
OL,14,Fburying evidence about poor care which
OL,15,Fresults in avoidable deaths.
OL,17,FThe NHS says it is investing #186
OL,18,Fmillion per year into growing the and
OL,19,Fstrengthening leadership - and is
OL,20,Fworking with trusts to make
OL,21,Fimprovements.
