OL,3,C'It's because we care': Families
OL,4,Cfighting for justice after maternity
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FThree weeks ago today, the details of
OL,8,Fyet another tragic death in maternity
OL,9,Fcare were revealed.
OL,11,FZachary Taylor-Smith was just 14 hours
OL,12,Fold when he died at the Royal
OL,13,FDerbyshire Hospital.
OL,15,FThe coroner found that staff missed
OL,16,Fmultiple opportunities to save his
OL,17,Fyoung life and that gross failures
OL,18,Famounted to neglect.
