OL,3,C'It's because we care': Families
OL,4,Cfighting for justice after maternity
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FHis mum Hannah said: "In the moment,
OL,8,Fwhen we got that conclusion, I felt a
OL,9,Flot of relief and I felt like the
OL,10,Fanger hit me days later.
OL,12,F"I couldn't even count how many
OL,13,Ffamilies we've spoken to whose baby
OL,14,Fdied due to negligence or neglect.
OL,16,F"I didn't realise there were any
OL,17,Fissues in maternity services prior to
OL,18,Fthis. And after reading Zach's Serious
OL,19,FIncident report, you just think, how
OL,20,Fis it? How is this happening? How does
OL,21,Fthis happen?"
