OL,3,C'It's because we care': Families
OL,4,Cfighting for justice after maternity
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FMore than a decade apart - Kate and
OL,8,FZachary suffered the same fate in the
OL,9,Fcare of Midlands maternity services.
OL,10,FNow their parents are united by a
OL,11,Fcommon grief and determination.
OL,13,FTim Taylor-Smith said: "We've been
OL,14,Fthrough every emotion you could
OL,15,Fpossibly lay on the table.
OL,17,F"We've been through anger and fear of
OL,18,Fwhat's going to come next year with
OL,19,Fthe inquest anything you could
OL,20,Fpossibly think.
OL,26,@uD@XOU
