OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,F"And then my world came crashing down
OL,8,Fand you don't care until you care. And
OL,9,Fthen it becomes your life's work to
OL,10,Ftry and prevent it from happening to
OL,11,Fanyone else.
OL,13,F"It's hard work and it's because we
OL,14,Fcare that we shout so loud and we need
OL,15,Fothers to to hear us."
